      <title>美国和日本结束对致命鱼鹰坠机事故的搜寻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/us-and-japan-conclude-search-in-fatal-osprey-plane-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和日本完成了对一架“鱼鹰”军用飞机及其在日本岛屿坠毁时丧生的八名飞行员的搜索、救援和打捞行动，促使五角大楼停飞了其倾转旋翼机机队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/us-and-japan-conclude-search-in-fatal-osprey-plane-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 00:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
