      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称历史表明特朗普新任期将构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/lagarde-says-history-suggests-a-trump-victory-would-be-a-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德警告称，回顾唐纳德·特朗普作为美国总统的第一个任期，人们会担心他可能在 2025 年重新掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/lagarde-says-history-suggests-a-trump-victory-would-be-a-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁审查预计将持续一年或更长时间，与预测相悖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/biden-review-of-us-steel-deal-seen-dragging-on-maybe-into-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国对新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的国家安全审查不太可能在今年年底结束，并且可能会延长至 2025 年，这一时间远远长于这些公司公开表示的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/biden-review-of-us-steel-deal-seen-dragging-on-maybe-into-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 18:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
